going negotiation of social, cultural, and geopolitical identities in the Chinese-speaking world.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aAction and adventure filmsxChinaxHong KongxChinaxChinaxHong KongxTaiwan. 0aAction and adventure filmsxChina. 0aAction and adventure filmsxTaiwan. 0aAction and adventure filmszChinazHong Kong. 0aAction and adventure filmszChina. 0aAction and adventure filmszTaiwan. 0aWomen heroes in motion pictures. 4aAsian Studies : Asian Studies. 4aCultural Studies : Cultural Studies. 4aFilm, Visual Culture, and Performing Arts : Film Studies. 4aGender and Sexuality : Gender Studies. 4aGender and Sexuality : Women's Studies. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143845250040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438452500423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438452500/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles